item.title: Captain Suite
item.dc:creator: admin
item.content:encoded:
Spread out in style in our spacious One Bedroom Captain Suite. Well-appointed with modern, nautical-inspired decor and luxurious amenities, our suites are the height of refinement and style.
A spacious and well designed suite with balcony facing the forest and garden
The suite is well-designed and well furnished, the bedroom and living room are not separated. In the living room includes: sitting area, desk, coffee table and a 'Nespresso' coffee maker. The bedroom includes: an 'Aminach Forest Mattress' which was designed especially for the resort, reading lamps and a closet. The suite also includes a grand bathroom.
The suite opens to a sun balcony with 2 patio lounge chairs, viewing the garden. There are Planters on both sides of the balcony.
Suite guests can watch free DVDs, all you need to do is choosing your favorite films from our collection (at the front desk).
